metadata.name: Gitcoin Impact Report
metadata.description:
This is an open edition collectible, commemorating our first-ever Impact Report featuring highlights from years of empowering communities to fund what matters. The Impact Report is a visual homage to the report, which includes all the major facts and figures plus deep-dive case studies into select grantees including Optimism, Uniswap, Shamba Network, Coin Center and many more. None of this would be possible without the commitment of builders and the support of partners throughout the years - we appreciate you!
